      "id": "5bc5705700d08c00135887dd",
      "text": "Positional Encoding",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666014,
      "updated": 1539666026
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc57069aff09e0000bb4b83",
      "text": "[Transformer]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666026,
      "updated": 1539666201
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc5710eaff09e0000bb4b85",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1bc1a16a113f46091aacb7f3fdcb92cd]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666191,
      "updated": 1539666191
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc57121aff09e0000bb4b86",
      "text": "https://arxiv.org/pdf/1706.03762.pdf ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666209,
      "updated": 1539666572
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc5728caff09e0000bb4b8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666572,
      "updated": 1539666572
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc5706baff09e0000bb4b84",
      "text": "要するにi個の回転する単位ベクトルで、それぞれの回転周期は",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666027,
      "updated": 1539666267
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc57183aff09e0000bb4b89",
      "text": "\t回転周期[$ 2\\pi]: [$ \\sin(pos), \\cos(pos)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666308,
      "updated": 1539666340
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc57125aff09e0000bb4b88",
      "text": "\t回転周期 [$ 10000 \\cdot 2\\pi]: [$ \\sin(pos / 10000), \\cos(pos / 10000)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666213,
      "updated": 1539666377
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc57125aff09e0000bb4b87",
      "text": "の間を等比級数的に刻んだものになっている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666213,
      "updated": 1539666397
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc586c1aff09e0000b3a2c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539671745,
      "updated": 1539671745
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc586c1aff09e0000b3a2c7",
      "text": "[位置]の概念を[数直線]的に捉えてしまいがちだが、これは位置を[循環]する値として表現している。だから無限に長い系列があると必ず「同じ位置」が繰り返すのだが、その周期が十分長いならば実用上の問題はない。地表だって実際は循環しているのに日常生活では直交座標だと思ってるしね。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539671745,
      "updated": 1539932092
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc571ebaff09e0000bb4b8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666411,
      "updated": 1539666411
    },
    {
      "id": "5bc571cbaff09e0000bb4b8a",
      "text": "入力に対してconcatするのではなく、足し合わせてしまうのだが、それで良いらしい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539666379,
      "updated": 1539666427
    },
